div2.p:
"There, if you'll have nuts I'll bring you nuts;
           I'll bring you lots of nuts, I will; I'll bring you a bushel of nuts,
           an' --some tomatuses."

"Sorry indeed to disturb you, Miss," observes the sheriff;
            "but you see, I've been searching and swearing of 'em all,
            and its only fair to serve all alike."
